name: CracklingFireforSleep
0:
”Alexa open cracklingfire”
”Alexa ask cracklingfire to play for 30 minutes”
”Alexa stop”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: crackling fire
des: Let the comforting sound of a crackling fire make you feel at peace! Get started by saying, 'Alexa, open Crackling Fire,' and enjoy a 30-minute session of sound. It's an excellent feature to use during sleep, for deep relaxation, meditation practices, or to help concentrate on your tasks.
